            "creation_date": 1342260747,
            "body": "<ol>\n<li><strong>Right click on Project -> Android Tools -> Fix Project Properties<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Go to <strong>menu -> Project -> Clean<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n<p>For that go to each java file import all required packages or try <code>CTRL + SHIFT + O<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>then resolve all errors in <code>RES<\/code> folder.<\/p>\n\n<p>Then it will generate <code>R.java<\/code> for you<\/p>\n\n<p>then <code>import yourpakagename.R;<\/code> where ever required. <\/p>\n\n<p>remove <code>import android.R;<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>hope this will help you<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 11482888,
            "question_id": 11482870
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fdd82a6a80426f76056d141d4e273149?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
