            "last_activity_date": 1342261965,
            "creation_date": 1342261400,
            "body": "<p>Place the sdk path in <strong>Window->Preference->android<\/strong>. <\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/7xrlD.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\">\nAnd then Click apply.\nIf you already do it. Then right click the project and goto <strong>Properties->android->select android version<\/strong><\/p>\n",
